Motivation
#19746 introduces radix tree on pd-decode side;
In PD disaggregation with radix cache enabled on the decode side, _pre_alloc() writes req_to_token_pool as [prefix_locs (0..pre_len) | delta_locs (pre_len..seq_len)]. When there is a prefix hit (pre_len > 0), prepare_for_prebuilt() incorrect
